I'm ready to love, yeah ♪</i>

28:35.380 --> 28:37.507
<i>♪ I love, I love
I'm ready to love, yeah ♪</i>

28:39.884 --> 28:44.264
<i>♪ I love, I love, I'm ready to
Ready to, ready to love ♪</i>

28:44.264 --> 28:46.391
- Yeah!
- Yeah!

28:46.391 --> 28:48.601
<i>♪ Ready to love, yeah ♪</i>

28:48.601 --> 28:52.897
<i>♪ You keep me awake
with your white lily smile ♪</i>

28:53.481 --> 28:57.068
<i>♪ Don't keep me watching
your charms all the while ♪</i>

28:58.278 --> 29:02.407
<i>♪ 'Cause as all the wise men say ♪</i>

29:02.407 --> 29:04.826
<i>♪ Grab it if it comes your way ♪</i>

29:05.243 --> 29:07.454
<i>Hey, Reynie. How's it going?</i>

29:08.037 --> 29:10.290
<i>This semester's off to a great start.</i>

29:10.290 --> 29:13.918
<i>Can't wait for your visit.
Everyone's excited to meet you.</i>

29:14.836 --> 29:16.713
<i>♪ Wo-ho-ho ♪</i>

29:21.009 --> 29:22.677
<i>Hey, Reynie. Kate here.</i>

29:22.677 --> 29:24.345
<i>Just wanted to drop you a note</i>

29:24.345 --> 29:27.056
<i>to let you know that we are back home
and back to work.</i>

29:28.933 --> 29:30.477
<i>Think we're finding a good groove.</i>

29:30.477 --> 29:33.897
<i>♪ Help my baby eyes
and open up the door ♪</i>

29:34.606 --> 29:38.651
<i>♪ You make me real
to everyone and everyday ♪</i>

29:38.651 --> 29:42.822
<i>♪ I, I thank the Lord
that you came along this way ♪</i>

29:42.822 --> 29:45.784
<i>♪ It's no more an illusion ♪</i>

29:45.950 --> 29:49.537
<i>You asked for a letter.
This fulfills that request.</i>

29:50.079 --> 29:52.332
<i>You're welcome. Constance.</i>

29:52.332 --> 29:56.503
<i>♪ I love, I love
I'm ready to love, yeah ♪</i>

29:57.003 --> 29:58.254
<i>♪ Oh ♪</i>

29:59.047 --> 30:00.548
<i>♪ Oh-oh ♪</i>

30:02.091 --> 30:07.388
<i>♪ I'm ready, ready, ready, ready to love ♪</i>

30:12.185 --> 30:15.230
Do old people do puzzles
to keep their mind fresh?

30:15.230 --> 30:17.482
Oh, hello.

30:17.482 --> 30:19.400
Some do, I'm sure.

30:19.901 --> 30:22.028
Science is pretty clear on the benefits.

30:23.029 --> 30:24.656
Then maybe...

30:26.491 --> 30:29.911
maybe you can find out where I come from?

30:30.662 --> 30:31.621
Oh.

30:33.248 --> 30:34.415
I'd be happy to try.

30:36.709 --> 30:38.545
And by the way, I am only 51.

30:38.545 --> 30:41.047
I know. It's disgusting.

30:41.047 --> 30:43.883
Ah... Well, I look 46.

30:46.177 --> 30:48.263
- That's a lot of luggage.
- Yes.

30:49.973 --> 30:51.474
I'm joining the society.

30:52.433 --> 30:55.103
- You are?
- Trust me, it's necessary.

30:55.103 --> 30:57.105
Turns out we have a sister.

31:02.694 --> 31:05.154
And she is not as nice as I am.
